{{Vgname|马基埃亚尔的传说|en=Tales of Maj'Eyal}} （简称''ToME4''）是一个由Nicolas Casalini（DarkGod）开发的[[开源|开源]]的[[Roguelike|Roguelike]][[电子游戏|电子游戏]]，并由Assen Kanev（Rexorcorum）与Raymond Gaustadnes（Shockbolt）操刀美工。它以Casalini早期制作的游戏[[Tales_of_Middle_Earth|Tales of Middle Earth]]为基础<ref>{{cite web|title=Roguelike Radio:Episode 18: ToME 4|url=http://www.roguelikeradio.com/2012/01/episode-18-tome4.html|accessdate=8 January 2013|date=10 January 2010|archive-date=2018-01-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6wT5rFOHs?url=http://www.roguelikeradio.com/2012/01/episode-18-tome4.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref> ，后者则以[[Angband_(video_game)|Angband]]为基础。<ref>{{cite web|title=Angband at oook.cz – Variant list|url=http://angband.oook.cz/variants.php?variant=tome|accessdate=9 January 2013|archive-date=2013-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130121133542/http://angband.oook.cz/variants.php?variant=tome|dead-url=no}}</ref>ToME 4的开发始于2009年，最早的正式版本发行于2012年。<ref name="Sykes">{{cite web|last=Sykes|first=Tom|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/12/18/tales-of-majeyal-is-released-despite-being-out-for-109-years/|title=Tales of Maj’Eyal is released, despite being out for 109 years|website=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|date=18 December 2012|accessdate=11 January 2013|archive-date=2014-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107110355/http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/12/18/tales-of-majeyal-is-released-despite-being-out-for-109-years|dead-url=no}}</ref>

马基埃亚尔的传说遵循[[GNU_GPL|GNU GPL]] 3许可证，在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[Mac_OS_X|Mac OS X]]以及[[Linux|Linux]]下均可免费下载运行。<ref name="Davison" /> 。同时，通过[[Steam_(software)|Steam]]<ref name="Davison">{{cite web|last=Davison|first=Pete|website=US Gamer|date=17 December 2013|accessdate=26 December 2013|title=Infinite Dungeons, Infinite Death: Tales of Maj'Eyal PC Review|url=http://www.usgamer.net/articles/infinite-dungeons-infinite-death-tales-of-majeyal-pc-review|archive-date=2015-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151109165936/http://www.usgamer.net/articles/infinite-dungeons-infinite-death-tales-of-majeyal-pc-review|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Steam">{{cite web|title=Tales of May'Eyal on Steam|website=[[Steam_(software)|Steam]]|url=http://store.steampowered.com/app/259680|accessdate=26 December 2013|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323205245/https://store.steampowered.com/app/259680/|dead-url=no}}</ref>或[[GOG.com|GOG]]<ref name="GOG Release">{{cite web|website=GOG|date=4 November 2014|accessdate=5 November 2014|title=Release: Tales of Maj'Eyal and Ashes of Urh'Rok expansion|url=http://www.gog.com/news/release_tales_of_majeyal_and_ashes_of_urhrok_expansion|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128115112/https://www.gog.com/news/release_tales_of_majeyal_and_ashes_of_urhrok_expansion|dead-url=no}}</ref>亦可购买。

==游戏性==

马基埃亚尔的传说是一款可定制界面、同时结合传统[[Roguelike|Roguelike]]快捷键与鼠标操作的地牢爬行类游戏。<ref name="diy" /> 与许多古老的Roguelike游戏不同，马基埃亚尔的传说使用全彩画面，几乎可完全用鼠标操作，并且玩家可通过不同的途径（如[[角色升级|角色升级]]）获得额外的生命，而非[[永久死亡|永久死亡]]。<Ref name="gi.biz"/>

马基埃亚尔的传说着力于充满策略的回合制战斗，以及自由的角色培养。游戏的发展很大程度上取决于玩家的决策与游戏水平。游戏开始前，玩家要在9个种族和25个职业（允许使用[[插件|插件]]拓展）中分别选择一个。一开始，并非所有种族与职业都可使用，有些必须要在游戏进程中解锁，<ref name="indiestatik">{{cite web|title=Tales Of Maj’Eyal Is The Best Roguelike You’ve Never Played, Now Released After Years In Beta|url=http://indiestatik.com/2012/12/17/tales-of-majeyal-released/|last=Tarason|first=Dominic|date=17 December 2012|website=Indie Statik|accessdate=8 January 2013|archive-date=2012-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121230204335/http://indiestatik.com/2012/12/17/tales-of-majeyal-released/|dead-url=no}}</ref>或借由捐赠、购买等方式解锁<ref name="Steam" />

玩家要在游戏中探索埃亚尔（Eyal）——一个充满传说、地牢与敌人的世界。游戏流程是非线性的，取决于玩家的计划和抉择，以及战斗技巧。

== 开发 ==

游戏引擎T引擎（T-Engne）使用[[C语言|C]]语言编写，并为基于网格的游戏提供了[[Lua_(programming_language)|Lua]]
语言的框架。该引擎支持诸多[[OpenGL|OpenGL]]特性，如[[粒子系统|粒子效果]]与[[着色器|着色器]]。2011年与2012年，T引擎被用于在七日Roguelike竞赛（Seven Day Roguelike Challenge）上开发游戏。<ref>{{cite web|title=2011 Seven Day Roguelike Challenge Evaluation|url=http://www.roguetemple.com/7drl/2011/|accessdate=14 January 2013|date=8 April 2011|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323201927/http://www.roguetemple.com/7drl/2011/|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|title=2012 Seven Day Roguelike Challenge Evaluation|url=http://www.roguetemple.com/7drl/2012/|accessdate=14 January 2013|date=9 May 2012|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324181702/http://www.roguetemple.com/7drl/2012/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

马基埃亚尔的传说亦可通过插件系统，获取新的图像、界面、游戏内容，或调整游戏平衡性。

